<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.5">
<l>veḷḷai nuṇmaṇaṟ koṇṭu ciṟṟil vicittirap paṭavītivāyt</l>
<l>teḷḷi nāṅka ḷiḻaitta kōla maḻitti yākilu muṉṟaṉmēl</l>
<l>uḷḷa mōṭi yuruka lallā lurōṭa moṉṟu milōṅkaṇṭāy</l>
<l>kaḷḷa māta vākē cavāvuṉ mukattaṉa kaṇka ḷallavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if You destroy the kōlam-drawing that is the small [sand] house</l>
<l>That we drew in the street with the fine, white sand that we sprinkled</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [everyone] is impressed,</l>
<l>we do not feel any anger against You, other than having [our] hearts</l>
<l rend="indent">suffer and melt, you see!</l>
<l>O sly Mādhava! Kesava! It is eyes that are on Your face, right?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
